data.description: Amazing four bedroom home in sought after Heritage Plantation. This home features a large, isolated master, oversized secondary bedrooms, huge bonus with ample storage, plus a study with built ins. Large back patio, and beautiful view of the lake from the front porch. New flooring and paint throughout most of the home, many updates including kitchen updates, roof and HVAC. The neighborhood boasts two pools, gym, tennis and basketball courts, ponds, and walking trails. Convenient to County Line Road and all of the schools and newer developments in Madison. Come and see all that this beautiful home has to offer.
